      "span_text": "The interpretation panel contains a number of scientific words and this, coupled with inadequate explanation of the weathering system, results in the current information not being comprehendible to a wide variety of tourists, considering their potential range in age, education, experience and cultural origin.  has discussed the importance of making geological information accessible to the general public and the need to accommodate a diverse tourist profile."
